呢隻風並唔係一個充分既理由證明佢講既野錯/係五毛㗎嘛，係咪？</span><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地正反都會講 所以要自己多D思考"},{"pid":"fd3a9eb8ee6bdf21246d5fead988dfd73f302075","tid":1628930,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:34:20.000Z","msg":"真 每個人都有自己意見<br />\n唔好一言不合就話人地係五毛 係風向撚 善用起底 認真思考下對方出發點係邊"},{"pid":"428439f5dbb293143bff78de7859c10db7a2ae08","tid":1628930,"uid":237785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc80763b87e8c4e888ea3667d0c481ef00083911","tid":1628930,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:32:01.000Z","msg":"和而不同先係民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且真理越辯越明<br />\n我相信集體智慧必需建基於充分討論，而唔係互屌三毛"},{"pid":"d3dbf8f6df9bbb51957fc1662052cf5b75f84dcd","tid":1628930,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf22bf47116cd53d01f9aee262cd2674639dd17","tid":1628930,"uid":164730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:35:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢排咁多人吹風話唔好吹風，就知有人好驚</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cc5b149b89cb2a445d06f89b5a9ab0406bef12","tid":1628930,"uid":237785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:35:14.000Z","msg":"推上熱門 等多d人睇到"},{"pid":"4e0df699e226d89a83c6b15c0c4168f91758e6b7","tid":1628930,"uid":298186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">願榮光歸香港</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"